<node id="Abdômen">
  <data key="d0">Abdômen</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The abdomen is a suitable site for insulin application, specifically the lateral right and left areas, maintaining a distance of three to four fingers from the navel.&lt;SEP&gt;Abdômen is a region of the body where insulin can be injected, but is not the preferred site for insulin absorption, especially for pregnant women.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-14a20edff579b0a517854d16cd546924&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-30e579d5ccfc0135f92c7582f294d15f</data>
