<node id="Bebê">
  <data key="d0">Bebê</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">The baby is a vulnerable individual whose well-being must be prioritized during insulin application.&lt;SEP&gt;The baby is affected by the mother's diabetes during pregnancy, with potential risks including being born large or requiring neonatal urinary tract infections (UTIs).</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-14a20edff579b0a517854d16cd546924&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e6f6de4abe268656fba04970b00cea11</data>
