<node id="Caroços">
  <data key="d0">Caroços</data>
  <data key="d1">category</data>
  <data key="d2">Lipohypertrophy is a condition characterized by the formation of nodules or lumps in the skin, often as a result of repeated insulin injections in the same area.&lt;SEP&gt;Caroços are small, localized areas of fat accumulation that can occur at injection sites, leading to insulin resistance and other complications.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-14a20edff579b0a517854d16cd546924&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39d6a3c2463013fd9e732773c88b8db5</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
