  <data key="d1">category</data>
  <data key="d2">Glicemia refers to the level of glucose in the blood, which is regulated by insulin.&lt;SEP&gt;Glycemia refers to blood glucose levels, which must be carefully managed during pregnancy to prevent complications.</data>
