<node id="Diabetes">
  <data key="d0">Diabetes</data>
  <data key="d1">condition</data>
  <data key="d2">Diabetes is a chronic condition that affects blood sugar regulation, requiring proper management and treatment, including insulin application and rodizio.&lt;SEP&gt;Diabetes is a chronic condition where the body is unable to regulate blood sugar levels effectively.&lt;SEP&gt;Diabetes is a medical condition characterized by high blood sugar levels, which can be further divided into type 1 and type 2 diabetes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e6f6de4abe268656fba04970b00cea11&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-30e579d5ccfc0135f92c7582f294d15f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84cbfc1493e013840892a69f8694a3ea</data>
