<edge source="Diabetes tipo 1" target="Diabetes tipo 2">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Diabetes tipo 1 is a condition where the body is unable to produce insulin due to an autoimmune response, while diabetes tipo 2 is a condition where the body is resistant to insulin and is unable to use it effectively.</data>
  <data key="d9">condition,insulin production</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-5b718276408c07c4ce95283bdfdf03de</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1768244577</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Rodízio" target="Profissional de saúde">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Rodízio is a method of rotating the injection sites to prevent lipodistrofia, which is recommended by a profissional de saúde.</data>
  <data key="d9">healthcare professional,method</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-5b718276408c07c4ce95283bdfdf03de</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1768244577</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Glicose" target="Hormônio">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Glicose is a type of sugar that is essential for the body's energy production, which is regulated by hormones produced by the pâncreas.</data>
  <data key="d9">chemical,hormone</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-5b718276408c07c4ce95283bdfdf03de</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
