</edge>
<edge source="Disglicemia" target="Vasos sanguíneos">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Vasos sanguíneos are the blood vessels that can be damaged by frequent fluctuations in blood glucose levels, leading to the development of vascular complications.</data>
